The most-widely known video that introduces Bitcoin.

The video was created following a bounty offer for an animated movie (1.1).  

The video was posted on YouTube on March 22, 2011 (1.2).

The bounty was awarded to JustMoon and the 8,511.96 BTC award was distributed on April 05, 2011 (1.3).

The award recipient created the [[Bitcoin_Marketing_Fund]] and donated most of the bounty award proceeds to the fund.

